flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 40: Escrow Authorization and Release Controls Flow

  Start[Escrow in held state]
  ReleaseSeen{Release already processed?}
  AutoCheck{Delivery confirmed + 48h elapsed?}
  AutoRelease[Auto-release escrow]

  ManualReq[Manual release request]
  RoleCheck{Requester is Finance Admin?}
  PolicyCheck{Policy allows release now?}
  DualGate{Sensitive case needs dual approval?}
  DualApproved{Second approver confirmed?}
  Approved[Manual release approved]
  Blocked[Release blocked + escalation]

  Dispute{Active dispute?}
  Freeze[Freeze funds until resolution]
  Audit[(Append immutable audit log)]
  NoOp[Return idempotent no-op]

  Start --> ReleaseSeen
  ReleaseSeen -- Yes --> NoOp --> Audit
  ReleaseSeen -- No --> Dispute
  Dispute -- Yes --> Freeze --> Audit
  Dispute -- No --> AutoCheck

  AutoCheck -- Yes --> AutoRelease --> Audit
  AutoCheck -- No --> ManualReq --> RoleCheck

  RoleCheck -- No --> Blocked --> Audit
  RoleCheck -- Yes --> PolicyCheck
  PolicyCheck -- No --> Blocked
  PolicyCheck -- Yes --> DualGate
  DualGate -- No --> Approved --> Audit
  DualGate -- Yes --> DualApproved
  DualApproved -- Yes --> Approved --> Audit
  DualApproved -- No --> Blocked --> Audit
